---
// About section with design system
---

<section id="sobre-el-evento" class="about-section">
  <div class="about-container">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="about-header" data-animate>
      <h2 class="about-title">
        ¿Qué es <span class="about-accent">COCHATECH?</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="about-text">
        COCHATECH es un evento de innovación de alto nivel que reúne talento global con desafíos locales auténticos. Somos un Hackathon único, diseñado para las necesidades de la ciudad y el país.
      </p>
      <p class="about-text">
        Durante 36-48 horas, equipos multidisciplinarios colaboran bajo mentorías de expertos para crear soluciones reales que impacten en la economía, tecnología y sociedad de nuestra región.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Feature Cards Grid -->
    <div class="about-grid">
      <!-- Card 1: Real Challenges -->
      <div class="about-card" data-animate data-animate-delay="0">
        <div class="about-card-icon about-card-icon-cyan">🎯</div>
        <h3 class="about-card-title">Retos Reales</h3>
        <p class="about-card-text">
          Problemas reales de empresas, instituciones y comunidades. No son ejercicios teóricos: tus soluciones pueden implementarse.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2: Active Mentors -->
      <div class="about-card" data-animate data-animate-delay="120">
        <div class="about-card-icon about-card-icon-yellow">🤝</div>
        <h3 class="about-card-title">Mentores Activos</h3>
        <p class="about-card-text">
          Expertos en negocios, tecnología, diseño y impacto social. Disponibles para guiar tu equipo en cada fase del hackathon.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3: Lasting Impact -->
      <div class="about-card" data-animate data-animate-delay="240">
        <div class="about-card-icon about-card-icon-white">🚀</div>
        <h3 class="about-card-title">Impacto Continuo</h3>
        <p class="about-card-text">
          El hackathon no termina el último día. Ofrecemos mentorías post-evento y oportunidades de inversión para ideas prometedoras.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  :root {
    --ds-bg-deep: #020b1c;
    --ds-text-primary: #ffffff;
    --ds-text-secondary: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
    --ds-text-muted: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.35);
    --ds-cyan: #00d2ff;
    --ds-cyan-dim: rgba(0, 210, 255, 0.15);
    --ds-cyan-glow: rgba(0, 210, 255, 0.4);
    --ds-yellow: #ffff00;
    --ds-yellow-dim: rgba(255, 255, 0, 0.12);
    --ds-glass-bg: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
    --ds-glass-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07);
    --ds-glass-bg-hover: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    --ds-glass-border-hover: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
    --ds-glass-blur: 16px;
    --ds-font: 'Inter', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
    --ds-fs-base: clamp(0.95rem, 0.8vw + 0.5rem, 1.0625rem);
    --ds-fs-sm: clamp(0.8rem, 0.6vw + 0.5rem, 0.875rem);
    --ds-fs-lg: clamp(1.15rem, 1.2vw + 0.6rem, 1.35rem);
    --ds-fs-xl: clamp(1.5rem, 2.5vw + 0.5rem, 2.25rem);
    --ds-fs-2xl: clamp(2rem, 4vw + 0.5rem, 3.25rem);
    --ds-radius-md: 10px;
    --ds-radius-lg: 16px;
    --ds-radius-xl: 24px;
    --ds-space-4: 1rem;
    --ds-space-5: 1.25rem;
    --ds-space-6: 1.5rem;
    --ds-space-8: 2rem;
    --ds-space-10: 2.5rem;
    --ds-space-16: 4rem;
    --ds-t-normal: 300ms cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
    --ds-shadow-md: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
    --ds-shadow-lg: 0 16px 48px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
  }

  .about-section {
    padding: var(--ds-space-16) clamp(1rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    background: var(--ds-bg-surface);
    font-family: var(--ds-font);
    position: relative;
  }

  .about-section::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 60px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--ds-bg-deep), transparent);
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .about-container {
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .about-header {
    margin-bottom: var(--ds-space-16);
  }

  .about-title {
    font-size: var(--ds-fs-2xl);
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: var(--ds-text-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--ds-space-8);
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .about-accent {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--ds-cyan), var(--ds-yellow));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  }

  .about-text {
    font-size: var(--ds-fs-base);
    color: var(--ds-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 55ch;
    margin-bottom: var(--ds-space-6);
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--ds-space-6);
  }

  .about-card {
    background: var(--ds-glass-bg);
    backdrop-filter: blur(var(--ds-glass-blur));
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(var(--ds-glass-blur));
    border: 1px solid var(--ds-glass-border);
    border-radius: var(--ds-radius-xl);
    padding: var(--ds-space-8);
    transition: all var(--ds-t-normal);
  }

  .about-card:hover {
    background: var(--ds-glass-bg-hover);
    border-color: var(--ds-glass-border-hover);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: var(--ds-shadow-lg);
  }

  .about-card-icon {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: var(--ds-radius-md);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--ds-space-5);
    border: 1px solid;
    transition: transform var(--ds-t-normal);
  }

  .about-card:hover .about-card-icon {
    transform: scale(1.15);
  }

  .about-card-icon-cyan {
    background: var(--ds-cyan-dim);
    border-color: rgba(0, 210, 255, 0.15);
  }

  .about-card-icon-yellow {
    background: var(--ds-yellow-dim);
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 0, 0.15);
  }

  .about-card-icon-white {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .about-card-title {
    font-size: var(--ds-fs-lg);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: var(--ds-text-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--ds-space-4);
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .about-card-text {
    font-size: var(--ds-fs-sm);
    color: var(--ds-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }
</style>
